data.description: Location, location, location - Motivated seller says bring an offer! This home is conveniently located for all your needs. Four bedrooms, 2.5 bath home with a 1st floor primary bedroom. All New kitchen cabinets with quartz countertops w/beveled edge, butcher block prep area, high end SS appliances, and farmhouse sink. Enjoy year-round relaxation in the four seasons room - roof and skylights replaced in 2021, Anderson windows, hot water heat throughout the home. Three additional generously sized bedrooms upstairs, finished rec room and game room in the finished basement. Boasts a spacious fenced yard providing privacy and security, oversized heated 3 car garage with 8' doors.  leaf gutter guard system, A/C replaced in 2022, H2O replaced in 2021, sump pump with watchdog system. Make an appointment for your private viewing today!    This house being sold in as-is condition. As-is means as-is.      All room sizes and information are not deemed to be guaranteed. Broker do your diligence.
